Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:18.34,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I have a big gun, I took it from my Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:21.79,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Sick with Justice, I just wanna feel you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:25.20,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm your angel, only a ring away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:28.55,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You make me violate you, no matter who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:38.67,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's all up to you, no one lives forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:42.26,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Been burn in the hell, by all those pigs out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.34,0:00:45.53,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's always been hell, from when I was born...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:48.72,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}They make me violate them, no matter who they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.72,0:00:52.26,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs79}Get down on your knees! Get a good head on your shoulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:55.69,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}If it's for your guys, go to the end of the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.69,0:00:59.00,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Do what you think, give it with dedication...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:02.27,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'll put out your misery!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:05.67,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You made a mess! For Christ sakes, this rotten world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:09.10,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Shit out of luck! Go with my vision!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:12.54,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Light up the fire! Right on the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:15.90,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Weapon... I have it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.94,0:01:24.48,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Weapon... I have it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.11,0:01:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be daybreak there soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.21,0:01:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea at daybreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.78,0:02:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only worthless students find\Nthat sort of thing appealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.86,0:02:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I do agree that this\Nwinter sky is disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.23,0:02:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, Okajima is\Nin the Sea of Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.43,0:02:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you prepare two plane tickets?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure. A business trip, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.77,0:02:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us go there as well,\Nto the Sea of Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Why the hell\Nshould I suffer like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock! You bastard! How much\Ndo you think a gun costs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They came here to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to go through this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for something the Department\NManager's involved in?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.57,0:03:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're missing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.74,0:03:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They wanna destroy that data\Ndisk, right? You're life is just...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M y life is just an accessory? Damn it!\NDamn it! Damn it! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You realize there's a torpedo in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Shut up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you find something\Nodd about this, Benny?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.62,0:03:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah, something's not right, Dutch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.79,0:03:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've totally stopped firing at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.26,0:03:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They could've easily turned\Nus into Swiss cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.36,0:03:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree. Something's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.40,0:03:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch! What's going on?\NWhere'd those guys go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Benny-boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:03:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've retreated to a distance\Nof about 5,000 meters behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and have been following us\Nwhile keeping that distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they after?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.32,0:04:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah, there's gotta{\i0}\N{\i1}be a reason.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.12,0:04:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's this waterway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's it! The waterway!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.06,0:04:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The path ahead to Belawan is\Nfilled with rocks and mangroves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As we proceed, the waterway\Nwill continue to narrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end we won't be able to\Nmake any evasive maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.80,0:04:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- There's no shame in running.\N- I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me I suck at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, guess I can't blame\Nyou if you did tell me so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no choice but to\Nevade to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.02,0:05:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we just enter the mouth of\Na river? This is a river, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.39,0:05:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we continue, we'll eventually\Nrun out of options to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We already know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've become completely trapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy's behind us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.57,0:05:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's looking down on us from\Nbehind, 5,000 meters from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that. A sunken ship.\NWhat a bad omen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.82,0:05:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is fine. This'll be our spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:06:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, go on. Go on and\Nkeep showing me your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.03,0:06:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, you guys\Nwill come back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then you'll hafta\Nface me. Hurry on back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And let's put an end to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.11,0:06:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch, they've stopped by the sunken\Nship. They're not chasing us anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no longer necessary for them\Nto waste their energy chasing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what that means.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dead end?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.65,0:06:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.65,0:06:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Meyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.28,0:06:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get so excited just imagining how\Nthey'll react in a crisis like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.12,0:07:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have no chance of beating us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll honeycomb the ship\Nwith our superior weaponry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.50,0:07:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly why I can't\Nwait to see how they'll react.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're the boring type\Nwho won't try to fight back...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then we'll just torture them to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no road ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to turn around and go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.95,0:07:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, he'll be waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M y gut tells me they have\Npurposely set up this ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They wanna finish this face to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.59,0:07:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, who's going to ring the bell?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes you'll find them around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.37,0:07:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So-called ancient bastards\Nwho think they're gunmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second! So the\Nonly choice is to die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.61,0:07:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well calm down, calm down, Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's call the local police!\NThat's better than getting...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.45,0:08:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not helping one\Nbit. Calm down, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.62,0:08:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Panicking isn't gonna solve anything.\NIf you wanna survive, use your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch. How about waiting\Nfor them to run outta fuel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.33,0:08:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bastards are from E.O. They'll come\Nto finish us off before that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did this have to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.64,0:08:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.35,0:08:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like a business paper. I want\Nto check on the stock prices.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.22,0:08:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right away, Mr. Kageyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.06,0:08:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How bad is the damage to the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not too bad, so far. I'm more\Nworried about that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If even a single bullet hits the torpedo,\Nwe'll end up flying to the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:09:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your own fault for keeping\Nthat thing on the ship, you dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.61,0:09:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I might have been\Nable to use it for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a waste, but maybe we\Nshould throw it overboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.55,0:09:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess we have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.68,0:09:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.02,0:09:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Dutch. Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go back to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.02,0:09:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand something, now that\NI've had time to think. Hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.23,0:09:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you disturb my thought process\NI'll let Revy nail you this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.93,0:09:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a shoot out, face to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can we have a shoot out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At most we have an anti-tank rifle.\NThey've got rocket missiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.11,0:09:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looked like the chopper\Nhad infra-red homing missiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't even come close.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.22,0:09:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so? We\Ndo have something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.09,0:09:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy. What did you give\Nhim to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To put it simply, it's a\Nhead on chicken race, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.46,0:10:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ship's speed and\Narmaments, that sunken ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we have everything we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.94,0:10:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.64,0:10:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...do you have in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.48,0:10:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you guys were just talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give them\Na flight to the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.59,0:10:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible. There's no\Nway we can pull that off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In theory, this ship is designed\Nto hydroplane...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At full speed we're only\Nin the water this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch. It's not as if we've\Ngot an alternate plan. I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The plan won't work unless\Nthey're right in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.61,0:10:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we count on that happening, Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.78,0:10:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're having a blast\Nchasing us around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.62,0:10:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite having a complete advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.19,0:10:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what's the reason for them\Nto restart the whole fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.40,0:11:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the type who imagines\Nhimself to be a gunman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.67,0:11:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we lure him into a chicken race,\Nhe'll be more than happy to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.97,0:11:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't guarantee you anything. From\Nthis point on, it's up to you as Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.81,0:11:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy we picked up is completely\Nout of his mind. He's gotta be insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.42,0:11:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.22,0:11:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And being excited is an important\Nthing, Rock. Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The radar's picked up something,\NCaptain. They're on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.27,0:11:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's accept their challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.24,0:11:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock! You know what\Nneeds to be done, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they launch a rocket, I fire the\Nsignal flare away from the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:12:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see the idiot. Revy! It's a\Nchicken race! Send them an invitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.36,0:12:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're firing at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.29,0:12:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.73,0:12:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! I accept the challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.93,0:12:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock! They're coming! Fire\Nthe infrared flare gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.54,0:12:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on the alpine course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you, get back into the cabin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They plan to use the\Nsunken ship as a shield?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.55,0:12:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's useless. Hey Meyer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.65,0:12:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.22,0:12:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we cross paths we'll\Nget them with a single shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna put an end to this duel!\NGet ready to get fucked, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.16,0:12:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,300 more feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,150 more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.17,0:12:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One hundred!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.41,0:12:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire number one! Fire number two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got fucked!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.52,0:13:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My head's still attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.79,0:13:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sunglasses aren't broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.23,0:13:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amen, hallelujah, peanut butter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.50,0:13:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fucking Christ has saved us this\Ntime. But I'll never do that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.44,0:13:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Benny, are you okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:14:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm alive, somehow. But\Nall our machinery is smashed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We need to fix it up. We're...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.14,0:14:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! How about Rock?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.58,0:14:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right over there, passed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.91,0:14:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He yelled out as we hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like one of William Holden's\Nlines from The Wild Bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at him. He looks so\Ncomfortable passed out like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.69,0:14:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, no kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.76,0:14:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that moment passed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.27,0:14:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...all the excitement the body's\Nadrenaline causes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...disappeared somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my boiling blood returned to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.88,0:14:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I, and what am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love smart work, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've gotta tell you,\Nyou guys look terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.70,0:15:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not going to a formal party.\NWe'll dress however we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Mr. Kageyama. We, from Hotel\NMoscow, have a code of honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.14,0:15:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I thought you were from the\NBougainvillea Trade Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.35,0:15:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We followed through in our own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.49,0:15:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There shouldn't be any grudges.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.59,0:15:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world is full of things\Nthat cannot be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's your turn to follow\Nthrough in your own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.90,0:15:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go over details at the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.51,0:15:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the good work,\NOkajima. Now, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.41,0:15:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okajima. What are you\Nwaiting for? Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss. Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.29,0:16:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I'm already dead.\NYou told me so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.00,0:16:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is...My name is Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? Then do as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.80,0:16:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get going, Fujiwara.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.31,0:16:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.59,0:16:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for making you\Ntalk with those idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'd consider it a great waste for\Na tough guy like you stay a Japonski.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.79,0:16:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to us anytime if\Nyou ever need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.13,0:16:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.24,0:16:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okajima...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.51,0:16:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's no longer an employee.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those eyes weren't the eyes of someone\Nwho could take on a managerial role.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.71,0:16:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, how'd things end up like\Nthis in such a short time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.18,0:16:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really care.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.32,0:17:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Rock. What will you do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no longer a hostage.\NAnd I've got nowhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. I know a place that\Ncould use a sailor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.50,0:17:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you be interested?\NIt's a delivery company...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At times they may take part\Nin illegal activity. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.73,0:17:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.20,0:17:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a boat that's blocking our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been blowing our\Nhorn but it won't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.79,0:18:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the amount of information\Nthat did get out was inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we were prepared for that much.\NThat was a job well done, Kageyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.33,0:18:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.68,0:18:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah, testing, testing...testing...um...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good morning, everybody{\i0}\N{\i1}aboard the St. Joan. Ah...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you wear that aloha\Nshirt I got for you at the market?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we're working right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.69,0:18:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. This is my job now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.97,0:18:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everybody aboard the St. Joan, I\N{\i1}apologize for the sudden request...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.50,0:19:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but I ask you to please stop your ship.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.54,0:19:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My personal opinion is that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...complying with the request as{\i0}\N{\i1}quickly as possible would be...um...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.35,0:19:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the best course of action!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dutch. The St. Joan has{\i0}\N{\i1}opened up its communications.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We've finally made contact.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.23,0:19:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what did they say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.40,0:19:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, "Unless you get out of our way,\Nwe will force our way through".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.67,0:19:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess it can't be helped.\NOkay, Benny. Revy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was an awfully long wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Time's up for being gentlemen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.91,0:19:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone, please take cover!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.68,0:19:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These moments make my\Nprehistoric blood awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.96,0:19:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have a rocket launcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand that over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.16,0:19:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen carefully, you dimwits!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.80,0:19:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My rockets are faster than mayday calls!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you don't want to end up{\i0}\N{\i1}as a ghost ship full of blood...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.73,0:20:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...then stop the ship, you bastards!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Benny-boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.15,0:20:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give notice to the guys at Lyun E.\NPan that we've taken the St. Joan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.55,0:20:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and that they'd better come get{\i0}\N{\i1}it before anyone starts a ruckus.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.66,0:20:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.53,0:20:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, John. Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takanori. How are things?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your studies for your entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.77,0:20:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're home today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.61,0:20:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About your daughter. She's been\Ngetting home late recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's only eighteen. Could\Nyou please talk to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.09,0:20:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.50,0:21:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.03,0:21:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What color was the sea of that\Nsouthern country...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.47,0:21:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you went to on your business trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.60,0:21:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Color of the sea? I can't really\Nsay. Daddy's been busy with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.44,0:21:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe no one will believe me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.18,0:21:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I've become a pirate\Nof the South Seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.79,0:21:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That huge ship was today's prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.42,0:21:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's get back to port before lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.96,0:21:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The China bowl at Kao Han...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.50,0:21:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...sure sells out quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:18.50,Black Lagoon Next Episode,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10\pos(980,916)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.03,0:23:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're being targeted by pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.60,0:23:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch! What's the background\Non our client?
